# nachweis demo trust anchors (placeholder)
#
# Real public trust anchors for the self-managed nachweis demo trust bundle are
# provisioned into this flavor at build/deployment time. Only public anchors ever
# live here; no CA private keys. See dev-plan.md, decision 6 (trust domain).
